--------------------------------------------------------------------

Virtual Environment Files (Essential to ignore)

--------------------------------------------------------------------

Explicitly ignore the user's environment folder

env/

Ignore common virtual environment names

venv/
.venv/

--------------------------------------------------------------------

Sensitive Authentication Files (MUST be ignored)

--------------------------------------------------------------------

Your Google API secrets downloaded from the console

credentials.json

The OAuth token generated during the authentication flow

token.json

--------------------------------------------------------------------

Temporary and Compiled Files (Good practice to ignore)

--------------------------------------------------------------------

Ignore temporary Python compiled files

pycache/
*.pyc
*.pyo

Ignore common IDE directories

.vscode/
.idea/